OL,3,COscar winning actress horrified at
OL,4,Csale of community theatre
OL,6,FOscar-winning actress Dame Judi Dench
OL,7,Fis horrified by the sale of a
OL,8,Fcommunity theatre in Kent by its
OL,9,Fcounty council.
OL,11,FThe Sarah Thorne Theatre is housed in
OL,12,Fthe Broadstairs Memorial Hall, which
OL,13,Fis due to be sold at auction today.
OL,15,FThe actress is backing a campaign
OL,16,Fopposing the sale, which is being led
OL,17,Fby local Labour councillors and the
OL,18,FLabour MP for East Thanet, Polly
OL,19,FBillington MP.
