OL,3,COscar winning actress horrified at
OL,4,Csale of community theatre
OL,6,FDame Judi Dench, who is a Trustee at
OL,7,Fthe theatre, said: "I was horrified to
OL,8,Fhear that the freehold of the building
OL,9,Fthat houses the Sarah Thorne Theatre
OL,10,Fhas been put up for auction by Kent
OL,11,FCounty Council (KCC).
OL,13,F"I understand that Michael Wheatley-
OL,14,FWard has a lease for five years, but
OL,15,Fthis sale would obviously put the
OL,16,Ffuture of the theatre in jeopardy.
OL,18,F"It would be a tremendous loss to the
OL,19,Flocal community, and every effort
OL,20,Fshould be made to secure its future."
