OL,6,FThe memorial is being sold as part
OL,7,Faims to target overspending, according
OL,8,Fto the Reform UK council.
OL,10,FIn a statement, Brian Collins, Deputy
OL,11,FLeader of KCC, said: "It is
OL,12,Fdisappointing that we have not been
OL,13,Fable to find enough local interest and
OL,14,Finvestment to support this community
OL,15,Fasset.
