OL,3,COscar winning actress horrified at
OL,4,Csale of community theatre
OL,6,F"The Sarah Thorne Theatre means a
OL,7,Fgreat deal to residents, and while I
OL,8,Fam proud that KCC has been able to
OL,9,Fsupport the group during the years
OL,10,Fthat KCC community learning and skills
OL,11,Foperated from the building, without a
OL,12,Fviable proposal, the council now has
OL,13,Fno choice but to move forward with the
OL,14,Fsale.
OL,16,F"I am fully aware of just how hard
OL,17,FCllr John Finch has been working to
OL,18,Ftry to find a solution. He has now
OL,19,Fexhausted all options, and no one has
OL,20,Fcome forward with a viable solution
OL,21,Fwithin the statutory timeframe."
