OL,6,FKent County Council says it has acted
OL,7,Fto safeguard the immediate future of
OL,8,Fthe Sarah Thorne Theatre by agreeing a
OL,9,F5 year lease allowing the trust which
OL,10,Fruns it to remain in the Memorial Hall
OL,11,Fdespite the sale.
OL,13,FIt also said the sale is statutory as
OL,14,Fthe building in Broadstairs is no
OL,15,Flonger used by KCC.
